<h1>AgeMap</h1>
<p>A visual app for managing ages and birthdays of family, friends, and colleagues.</p>
<p>Place people on a graph sorted by age, manage family trees, and get birthday reminders — all in one app.</p>

<h2>Key Features</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Age Map</strong> — Visualize people sorted by age on an interactive graph with pinch-zoom and pan</li>
  <li><strong>Family Tree</strong> — Display parent-child, spouse, and sibling relationships graphically</li>
  <li><strong>Groups</strong> — Organize people by family, friends, work, etc. with custom colors</li>
  <li><strong>Birthday Reminders</strong> — Push notifications at D-30, D-7, D-1, and D-day</li>
  <li><strong>Moments</strong> — Record gifts and memories by year with photo attachments</li>
  <li><strong>Backup & Restore</strong> — Safely store people, relationships, photos, and settings as a ZIP file</li>
</ul>

<h2>Additional Details</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Lunar birthday input supported (auto-converted to solar)</li>
  <li>Zodiac sign, birthstone, and oriental zodiac displayed automatically</li>
  <li>Precise age calculation in years, months, and days</li>
  <li>Set yourself as "Me" to appear in all groups automatically</li>
</ul>

